  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 59",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Sansa IV</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n659 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_28\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 28\">Sansa III</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_58\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 58\">Tyrion VII</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sansa IV</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_60\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 60\">Tyrion VIII</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_61\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 61\">Sansa V</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_59&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a> has learned from <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a> the fate of her <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">brother</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Tully\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Catelyn Tully\">mother</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a>. She and her husband join many other guests at the Queen’s Ballroom to give <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey</a> his wedding gifts. It is a new year, the 300th since <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_Conquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"War of Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>, and Joffrey’s wedding is that night. Tyrion presents his nephew with a copy of Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Kaeth\" title=\"Kaeth\">Kaeth</a>’s <a href=\"/index.php/Lives_of_Four_Kings\" title=\"Lives of Four Kings\">Lives of Four Kings</a>, one of only four copies in existence written by Kaeth himself. <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan</a> tells the King it is \"A book every king should read.\" Joffrey is disappointed with the gift, and hacks the book in half with the <a href=\"/index.php/Widow%27s_Wail\" title=\"Widow&#39;s Wail\">Valyrian sword</a> his <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">grandfather</a> had just given him. Joffrey remarks that he is no stranger to <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a>, and also that Tyrion owes him another gift.  Tyrion suggests a Valyrian dagger with a <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonbone\" title=\"Dragonbone\">dragonbone</a> hilt, which seems to unsettle Joffrey for a moment before he says it is a good idea but wants one with a gold hilt instead. \n</p><p>Later, back in their rooms, Sansa tells Tyrion that she would rather not know how Robb and her mother had perished, and Tyrion promises that he will say no more.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_59&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Tully\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Catelyn Tully\">Catelyn Tully</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kaeth\" title=\"Kaeth\">Kaeth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ellaria_Sand\" title=\"Ellaria Sand\">Ellaria Sand</a></li></ul>\n</div>\t\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_59&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/War_of_Conquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"War of Conquest\">War of Conquest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lives_of_Four_Kings\" title=\"Lives of Four Kings\">Lives of Four Kings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Widow%27s_Wail\" title=\"Widow&#39;s Wail\">Widow's Wail</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dragonbone\" title=\"Dragonbone\">Dragonbone</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_59&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from Aol member vbkorik27 previously at<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2013/07/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-36\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords, Part 36</a>. Analyses and summary of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403091549\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.045 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.181 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 242/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1096/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7932/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1269/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.120/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.29 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memor